{"tid":1392388,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工處推網上職安健投訴平台","createTime":"2019-07-31T17:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T01:13:39.000Z","uid":206097,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c8aa1d4a4c04a63dedbe9f63d157c19ef363a3","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:20:20.000Z","msg":"香港建造業奪命工業意外頻生，為加強工人的職安健意識，勞工處今日(19日)推出網上職業安全及健康投訴平台，讓僱員及公眾人士透過流動電子裝置或電腦，更方便地就工作地點的不安全作業模式或環境狀況，以電子表格形式向勞工處作出舉報。處方強調，除在法例特定的情況下，勞工處不會披露投訴人的資料，亦不會披露因收到投訴而到訪某工作地點。<br />\n網上平台可讓投訴人更快捷及方便地就職安健不當作業作投訴，令勞工處能夠盡快跟進以防止意外發生。投訴人可以透過智能電話、平板電腦等流動電子裝置，到勞工處網頁： <a href=\"http://www.labour.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGDsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=bf68c6f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.labour.gov.hk</a> 填寫電子表格作出舉報，並可上傳相片、影片或錄音檔案。<br />\n勞工處收到投訴後，會因應投訴的性質及內容，盡快派員巡視相關的工作地點，作出針對性的調查及跟進，處方亦已適當地安排人手以配合這些調查跟進工作。"},{"pid":"1c74b276f70b6b60f2ceeab20c45a69433f00f30","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T17:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9479e429632e9bb987a08bc8fd107d5b75f728ed","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637207b804ff076766c9f547528ff99a86d45e76","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7e47ab02fb5a7114a61949f7f6e3b21eafe9f0","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4dd130096a860ef5906b9d0db91d6b9b20f57c6","tid":1392388,"uid":206097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci